Dialogue: 2,0:01:28.32,0:01:33.06,1080EN,,0,0,0,,Eclipse will appear to last for over seven minutes as they fly eastwards. Each
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.06,0:01:37.40,1080CN,,0,0,0,,每次日食在地球上留下的影子都不同，这取决于月球
Dialogue: 2,0:01:33.06,0:01:37.40,1080EN,,0,0,0,,solar eclipse follows a different course over the earth dictated by the moon's
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.40,0:01:42.42,1080CN,,0,0,0,,与地球、太阳的相对位置。同时也导致
